### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/
Accept: application/json

###

### ============================================
### STEP 1: Upload PDFs First
### ============================================

### Upload One PDF
POST {{baseUrl}}/upload_pdfs
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=UploadBoundary

--UploadBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="files"; filename="sample.pdf"
Content-Type: application/pdf

< {{pdfPath}}
--UploadBoundary--

###

### Upload Two PDFs
POST {{baseUrl}}/upload_pdfs
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=UploadBoundary

--UploadBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="files"; filename="sample-1.pdf"
Content-Type: application/pdf

< {{pdfPath}}
--UploadBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="files"; filename="sample-2.pdf"
Content-Type: application/pdf

< {{pdfPath2}}
--UploadBoundary--

###

### ============================================
### STEP 2: Ask Questions After Upload
### ============================================

### Ask a Question Using Variable
POST {{baseUrl}}/ask_question
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

question={{question}}

###

### Ask a Direct Custom Question
POST {{baseUrl}}/ask_question
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

question=List the most important medical points from the uploaded document.

###

### Ask About Diagnosis
POST {{baseUrl}}/ask_question
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

question=What diagnosis information is mentioned in the document?

###

### Ask About Treatment
POST {{baseUrl}}/ask_question
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

question=What treatment options are discussed?

###

### Ask for Summary
POST {{baseUrl}}/ask_question
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

question=Provide a brief summary of the key findings in the document.

